rComments: LA101 was easy and interesting. Weekly quizes on name of site, location and designer name, but they are super easy. Final paper is pretty easy as well. Using quizlet helped a lot with remembering the sites. Expect some readings. Lecture slides are purely visual, with little words. Meets for 1.5 hours once a week. EASY A!!
Cares a lot about his students. Materials for this course are interesting and easy. Just take this class, review the handouts before quizzes and final, and you will be fine.
His enthusiasm for landscape architecture is contagious. Take this class!
Love this guy. Can't get enough of his class. Had no idea landscape architecture encompassed so much. Just gives a quiz every class which is easy if you memorize the stuff.
awesome, understanding guy. Will help you with things outside of class with a passion and is always interested in what you have to say.

Really nice class.  Same setup every lecture, slideshow of pics while he discusses the weeks topic then a quiz on the previous weeks photos.  Alot of Memorization needed.  No hw, just weekly quizzes and the final, THATS IT!
Hot. Spicy. Stimulating. Enticing. Provocative. Specific. General. He moves like a sceptor  with a waft of genius betraying his trail.
